summary: This `genreshorror.html` file contributes to the system by providing a dedicated page for the Horror movie genre. It includes a header with links to the home page, about page, and contact page, allowing the user to easily navigate between different sections of the website. The file also displays a list of horror movie posters that the user can click on to navigate to specific movie pages. The use of CSS and JavaScript enhances the interactive elements and aesthetics of the page.
